Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:45.64,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.67,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:49.71,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.40,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,A blueprint of the airship,\NWhite Silver, was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:01.68,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only a few days until\Nthe maiden voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:04.72,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it and what\Nare their intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:08.62,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,The shining silver airship, White Silver,\Ntook off with Holmes in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:11.96,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,and so begins the\Nmystery in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:17.23,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.55,0:24:22.47,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase the airship, White Silver!
